ingredients: ENRICHED BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR (FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (INTERSTERIFIED SOYBEAN OIL, HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN OIL). CONTAINS 2% OF LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: BAKING POWDER (SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE, POTASSIUM BICARBONATE, SODIUM BICARBONATE, CALCIUM SULFATE, CORN STARCH, AMMONIUM GLUTAMATE, ENZYME) SALT, POTASSIUM SORBATE, CALCIUM PROPIONATE, MONOGLYCERIDES, FUMARIC ACID, TARTARIC ACID, DOUGH CONDITIONER (SODIUM METABISULFITE).
